{"tid":598853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇人講?]連環火災後　南生圍昨再現機油膠筒　鄺俊宇：警方需盡快揪出縱火者","createTime":"2018-03-20T02:09:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T02:09:56.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9625a1bfb03ee10e50ee3eab61ce80da61031d62","tid":598853,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T02:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/29357153_10155575808359685_5421894809315105756_n_x3ZTb_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F29357153_10155575808359685_5421894809315105756_n_x3ZTb_1200x0.jpg&h=aef19940&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元朗南生圍近日接連發生火警，警方已列作縱火案調查。民主黨鄺俊宇表示，再收到市民舉報，<strong>指昨天在南生圍發現一載著疑似機油的白色塑膠筒</strong>，感到事有蹺蹊，已於昨日黃昏報警。<br />\n<br />\n鄺俊宇表示，據悉警方已向該名市民錄取口供。鄺俊宇指，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">繼日前有市民舉報案發時有可疑人物後，再有市民發現可疑的易燃物料，若怪火屬人為，警方需要盡快揪出縱火人士。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鄺俊宇又指，將聯同《萬人聯署，決不讓南生圍淪陷》行動組，計劃於下週日於南生圍發動保衛行動，促社會關注保育南生圍，認為大家已無法容忍南生圍繼續被人不斷破壞。<br />\n<br />\n南生圍上周初爆連環火災，鄺俊宇早前已收到市民舉報，稱當日事發時在附近看到有兩、三個行跡可疑，「戴Cap帽、戴口罩」的中年男子，對方更加問該名市民是否記者，隨後附近就有地方起火。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E9%80%A3%E7%92%B0%E7%81%AB%E7%81%BD%E5%BE%8C-%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D%E6%98%A8%E5%86%8D%E7%8F%BE%E6%A9%9F%E6%B2%B9%E8%86%A0%E7%AD%92-%E9%84%BA%E4%BF%8A%E5%AE%87-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E9%9C%80%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%E6%8F%AA%E5%87%BA%E7%B8%B1%E7%81%AB%E8%80%85/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%2592%25B0%25E7%2581%25AB%25E7%2581%25BD%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%259C%258D%25E6%2598%25A8%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E8%2586%25A0%25E7%25AD%2592-%25E9%2584%25BA%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%25AE%2587-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%259C%2580%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E6%258F%25AA%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25B8%25B1%25E7%2581%25AB%25E8%2580%2585%2F&d=C88rzUCsV2hIq0hYYhme%2FSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=23f1aafb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%2592%25B0%25E7%2581%25AB%25E7%2581%25BD%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%259C%258D%25E6%2598%25A8%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E8%2586%25A0%25E7%25AD%2592-%25E9%2584%25BA%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%25AE%2587-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%259C%2580%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E6%258F%25AA%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25B8%25B1%25E7%2581%25AB%25E8%2580%2585%2F&h=81cccfca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E9%80%A3%E7%92%B0%E7%81%AB%E7%81%BD%E5%BE%8C-%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D%E6%98%A8%E5%86%8D%E7%8F%BE%E6%A9%9F%E6%B2%B9%E8%86%A0%E7%AD%92-%E9%84%BA%E4%BF%8A%E5%AE%87-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E9%9C%80%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%E6%8F%AA%E5%87%BA%E7%B8%B1%E7%81%AB%E8%80%85/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/1618615668224047/?t=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F1618615668224047%2F%3Ft%3D0&d=C88rzUCsV2hIq0hYYhme%2FSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=983e3d03\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/1618615668224047/?t=0</a>"}]}